cff-version: 1.2.0
title: PERSEUS Forest Intelligence
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Aaron
    family-names: Weiskittel
    email: aaron.weiskittel@maine.edu
    affiliation: "Center for Research on Sustainable Forests, University of Maine"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2972-0298"
abstract: >-
  CONUS multi-model forest-carbon explorer covering all 48 conterminous states
  with deep focal coverage for Maine, Indiana, and Georgia (plus multi-engine
  series for Minnesota, Oregon, Washington, and Idaho). Built on the perseus_db
  carbon-pool-harmonized database. Static React + Vite + MapLibre application
  deployed via GitHub Pages.
repository-code: "https://github.com/holoros/perseus-forest-intelligence"
